    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            inputClick();
            inputBlur();
            var ajaxImage = "<div class=\"ajaxLoadingInfo\"><img src=\"/images/ajax-loader.gif\" class=\"ajaxLoadVMFA\" alt=\"loading\" /><br/><p>Loading</p></div>";
            $.ajax({
                url: '/Handlers/CalendarCategories.ashx?action=ShowCalendarCategories',
                cache: false,
                success: function (data) {
                    $('#calCategories').html(data);
                },
                error: function (data) {
                    $('#calCategories').html(data);
                }
            });
            $('#calCategories a').live('click', function () {
                $('#calendarBox').html(ajaxImage);
                $(this).parent("li").toggleClass('selected');
                var selectedIds = selectedCalendarCat();
                var selectedNames = selectedCatName();
                if (selectedIds != undefined) {
                    $('#clr').show();
                }
                $.ajax({
                    url: '/Handlers/CalendarCategories.ashx?action=FilterCalendarItems&calendar_Catids=' + selectedIds + '&startDate=' + $('#ctl00_phContent_startDate_tbDate').val() + '&endDate=' + $('#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate').val() + '&calendar_Catnames=' + selectedNames,
                    cache: false,
                    success: function (data) {
                        $('#calendarBox').html(data);
                    },
                    error: function (data) {
                        $('#calendarBox').html(data);
                    }
                });
            });
            $('#clr').click(function () {
                $('#clr').hide();
                $('#calCategories li').removeClass('selected');
                $('#calendarBox').html(ajaxImage);
                $.ajax({
                    url: '/Handlers/CalendarCategories.ashx?action=FilterCalendarItems&calendar_Catids=&calendar_Catnames=&startDate=' + $('#ctl00_phContent_startDate_tbDate').val() + '&endDate=' + $('#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate').val(),
                    cache: false,
                    success: function (data) {
                        $('#calendarBox').html(data);
                    },
                    error: function (data) {
                        $('#calendarBox').html(data);
                    }
                });
            });
            $('#btnGo').click(function () {
                $('#calendarBox').html(ajaxImage);
                $('#clr').hide();
                var selectedIds = selectedCalendarCat();
                var selectedNames = selectedCatName();
                if (selectedIds != undefined) {
                    $('#clr').show();
                }
                $.ajax({
                    url: '/Handlers/CalendarCategories.ashx?action=CustomDates&calendar_Catids=' + selectedIds + '&startDate=' + $('#ctl00_phContent_startDate_tbDate').val() + '&endDate=' + $('#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate').val() + '&calendar_Catnames=' + selectedNames,
                    cache: false,
                    success: function (data) {
                        $('#calendarBox').html(data);
                    },
                    error: function (data) {
                        $('#calendarBox').html(data);
                    }
                });
            });
        });
        function selectedCalendarCat() {
            var calendarCatIds;
            $("#calCategories li").each(function () {
                if ($(this).hasClass('selected')) {
                    if (calendarCatIds == undefined) {
                        calendarCatIds = $(this).attr('id');
                    }
                    else {
                        calendarCatIds += "," + $(this).attr('id');
                    }
                }
            });
            return calendarCatIds;
        }
        function selectedCatName() {
            var calendarCatNames = "";
            $("#calCategories li").each(function () {
                if ($(this).hasClass('selected')) {
                    if ($(this).attr('id') != -1 && $(this).attr('id') != 0) {
                        if (calendarCatNames == "") {
                            calendarCatNames = $(this).text();
                        }
                        else {
                            calendarCatNames += ", " + $(this).text();
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
            return calendarCatNames;
        }
        function inputClick() {
            var image = "<img src=\"/images/ico-vmfa-close.gif\" alt=\"close calendar\" height=\"20\" width=\"20\" />"
            $("input").focus(function () {
                $(this).parent(".DatePickerContainer").append("<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" title=\"Close Date Picker\" class=\"closeCalendarVmfa\">" + image + "</a>");
            });
            $("input").blur(function () {
                $(".closeCalendarVmfa").remove();
               
            });
        }
        var intervalBlur = null;
       
        function inputBlur() {
            $("#ctl00_phContent_startDate_tbDate").blur(function () {
                var endDateValue = $("#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate").val();
                if (endDateValue == "") {
                    intervalBlur = setInterval(function () { modifyDate() }, 400);
                }

                //$("#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate").datepicker("setDate", date);
            });
        }
        function modifyDate() {
            var date = $("#ctl00_phContent_startDate_tbDate").val();
            var endDateValue = $("#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate").val();
            $("#ctl00_phContent_endDate_tbDate").val(date);
            clearInterval(intervalBlur);
            //alert(date);
        }
    </script>
